        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Gorgon's breath is a fine powder that can easily enter living creatures' bloodstreams through their lungs before binding to mucous membranes and causing any nearby soft tissues to harden.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">A</span> Interact (Inhaled)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"32\" data-pf2-traits=\"alchemical,consumable,inhaled,poison\" data-pf2-label=\"Gorgon's Breath DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span></p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 round</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed} 1 (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r 4d6 #bludgeoning]]{4d6 bludgeoning damage} and slowed 1 (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Petrified]{Petrified} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> petrified permanently</p>"
